S. Korea to Act to Stabilize Markets When Needed, Bahk Says

-- B y   W i l l i a m   S i m
-- 
2011-10-04T23:09:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/s-korea-to-act-to-stabilize-markets-when-needed-bahk-says.html
South Korea ’s government will act to
stabilize the financial markets when needed, Finance Minister
Bahk Jae Wan said at a government meeting today. The nation’s
exports may be hurt by a global economic slowdown, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
